data.description: Move in ready 3 bedroom 2 bath vinyl home with an oversized 2 car garage with up to $3000 in upgrade allowance at closing. Most areas have been freshly painted and all kitchen appliances remain. Sitting on over a half acre,the front yard offers plenty of shade with matured trees and a large covered front porch. The back yard is fully fenced in with a large deck. Would make a great starter home! The home also comes with a free one year home warranty. New water heater Dec 2023.
